items.title: Zelensky Chooses Applause From Democrats Over Survival

items.title: Wyoming Gov. Mark Gordon Refuses To Say If He’ll Sign A Bill Requiring Proof Of Citizenship For Elections
items.description: Gov. Mark Gordon won't say if he'll sign a bill requiring Wyoming residents to provide proof of citizenship when registering to vote.
